children.text: The builder has not provided a 75mm (minimum) gap under the Hebel panels to the ground, which the manufacturer warns will cause damage to the Hebel panels.
The Hebel Power Panel external wall design and installation instructions state that
â€˜All garden beds and /or finished soil line must remain a minimum of 75mm below the bottom of the finished rendered wall' .
The ground levels must be immediately rectified to prevent failure of the Hebel system, prior to works in this area proceeding any further.
